<sentences>
    <sentence>
        <content>关山难越,谁悲失路之人;萍水相逢,尽是他乡之客。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>路漫漫其修远兮,吾将上下而求索。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>落霞与孤鹜齐飞,秋水共长天一色。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>悟已往之不谏,知来者之可追。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>不以物喜,不以己悲。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>相看两不厌,唯有敬亭山。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>两情若是久长时,又岂在朝朝暮暮。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>大漠沙如雪,燕山月似钩。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>人生自古谁无死,留取丹心照汗青。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>但使主人能醉客,不知何处是他乡。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>锄禾日当午,汗滴禾下土。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>谁言寸草心,报得三春晖。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>醉翁之意不在酒,在乎山水之间也。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>长风万里送秋雁,对此可以酣高楼。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>宁可枝头抱香死,何曾吹落北风中。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>黄河远上白云间,一片孤城万仞山。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>羌笛何须怨杨柳,春风不度玉门关。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>天青色等烟雨,而我辈则多欢颜。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>无可奈何花落去,似曾相识燕归来。</content>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
        <content>清晨入古寺,初日照高林。</content>
    </sentence>
</sentences>